In the Matter of Attorneys in Violation of Judiciary Law § 468-a. Michael L. Ziegler, Admitted in 1976, at a Term of the Appellate Division, Second Department.

[— NYS2d —]

—Motion granted and the unpublished order of this Court entered on May 6, 1999 (M-344.683) is recalled and vacated and the Opinion Per Curiam filed therewith is amended to vacate so much thereof as pertains to the above-named respondent. No opinion. Concur — Ellerin, P. J., Nardelli, Williams, Mazarelli and Saxe, JJ.
